# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GeekBid — Root Environment Reference
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# This project has TWO env files you need to set up:
#
# 1. backend/.env      → Copy from backend/.env.example
#    (MongoDB, JWT, Razorpay, service ports)
#
# 2. web/.env.local    → Copy from web/.env.example
#    (MongoDB, NextAuth, Google OAuth, Razorpay)
#
# Quick start:
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
#   cp web/.env.example web/.env.local
#   # Then fill in your credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
